  "texts": [
    "Thus, we considered another statistical test suited for this kind of data in this paper.",
    "This statistical test is called the Kruskal-Wallis test.",
    "The Kruskal-Wallis test is a non-parametric alternative to ANOVA.",
    "Since it does not rely on assumptions of homogeneity of variances or normality and is robust to violations of these assumptions, the Kruskal-Wallis test is the most appropriate statistical test.",
    "This decision was made to ensure the validity of our findings and to accurately assess the differences between groups."
  ],
